<?xml version="1.0" encoding="utf-8" standalone="yes"?><rss version="2.0" xmlns:atom="http://www.w3.org/2005/Atom"><channel><title>RKNN on Shrond's Log</title><link>https://dasia373.github.io/tags/rknn/</link><description>Recent content in RKNN on Shrond's Log</description><generator>Hugo -- gohugo.io</generator><language>zh-cn</language><copyright>© 2026 工蜂</copyright><lastBuildDate>Fri, 12 Jun 2026 10:00:00 +0800</lastBuildDate><atom:link href="https://dasia373.github.io/tags/rknn/index.xml" rel="self" type="application/rss+xml"/><item><title>基于 RK3588 的 IMX415 低延迟 AI 视频推流系统</title><link>https://dasia373.github.io/posts/imx415-rtsp%E4%BD%8E%E5%BB%B6%E8%BF%9Fai%E8%A7%86%E9%A2%91%E6%8E%A8%E6%B5%81%E7%B3%BB%E7%BB%9F/</link><pubDate>Fri, 12 Jun 2026 10:00:00 +0800</pubDate><guid>https://dasia373.github.io/posts/imx415-rtsp%E4%BD%8E%E5%BB%B6%E8%BF%9Fai%E8%A7%86%E9%A2%91%E6%8E%A8%E6%B5%81%E7%B3%BB%E7%BB%9F/</guid><description>基于 RK3588 / IMX415 摄像头，实现 1080p@30fps RTSP 推流，并集成 person + helmet 双模型实时检测。从零调试到「稳定 30fps + 300–400ms 端到端延迟 + AI 异步推理无顿挫」的完整记录。</description></item><item><title>阶段6 — 延迟优化：模型异步推理</title><link>https://dasia373.github.io/posts/6-%E5%BB%B6%E8%BF%9F%E4%BC%98%E5%8C%96-%E6%A8%A1%E5%9E%8B%E5%BC%82%E6%AD%A5%E6%8E%A8%E7%90%86/</link><pubDate>Thu, 11 Jun 2026 16:00:00 +0800</pubDate><guid>https://dasia373.github.io/posts/6-%E5%BB%B6%E8%BF%9F%E4%BC%98%E5%8C%96-%E6%A8%A1%E5%9E%8B%E5%BC%82%E6%AD%A5%E6%8E%A8%E7%90%86/</guid><description>双 worker 异步推理架构，单槽覆盖策略，端到端延迟 500ms → 300–400ms，周期性顿挫消除。</description></item><item><title>阶段3 — 接入 helmet 模型</title><link>https://dasia373.github.io/posts/3-%E6%8E%A5%E5%85%A5helmet%E6%A8%A1%E5%9E%8B/</link><pubDate>Wed, 10 Jun 2026 10:00:00 +0800</pubDate><guid>https://dasia373.github.io/posts/3-%E6%8E%A5%E5%85%A5helmet%E6%A8%A1%E5%9E%8B/</guid><description>接入 helmet 模型绑定 NPU core1，双模型分核并行，通过错峰调度（offset=3、interval=12）避免同帧推理卡顿。</description></item><item><title>阶段2 — 接入 person 模型</title><link>https://dasia373.github.io/posts/2-%E6%8E%A5%E5%85%A5person%E6%A8%A1%E5%9E%8B/</link><pubDate>Tue, 09 Jun 2026 20:00:00 +0800</pubDate><guid>https://dasia373.github.io/posts/2-%E6%8E%A5%E5%85%A5person%E6%A8%A1%E5%9E%8B/</guid><description>接入 person RKNN 模型绑定 NPU core0，验证同步推理掉帧，实现跳帧推理+缓存结果策略，帧率恢复到约 29.3fps。</description></item></channel></rss>